summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1889, for the improvement of Mary Avenue Northwest, in the City of Seattle, from West Seventieth Street to West Seventy-fifth Street, by grading and curbing the same, under Ordinance No. 19557, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
